it's actually nice.

302
00:14:16,240 --> 00:14:17,510
You know,

303
00:14:18,000 --> 00:14:19,240
there is this saying,

304
00:14:19,240 --> 00:14:21,320
"It's better to travel than to read."

305
00:14:21,750 --> 00:14:23,840
It's crucial for them to study and read,

306
00:14:23,840 --> 00:14:24,960
but it's good for them

307
00:14:24,960 --> 00:14:25,840
to go out

308
00:14:25,840 --> 00:14:26,790
and see the world.

309
00:14:26,790 --> 00:14:27,480
I think

310
00:14:27,790 --> 00:14:29,030
