322
00:14:42,510 --> 00:14:43,240
You're all contributing,

323
00:14:43,240 --> 00:14:44,240
what about me?

324
00:14:44,240 --> 00:14:44,840
Guan.

325
00:14:45,600 --> 00:14:46,240
