328
00:14:49,670 --> 00:14:50,440
What is it?

329
00:14:50,440 --> 00:14:51,630
With the kids gone,

330
00:14:51,630 --> 00:14:53,720
the wonton shop will be shorthanded
during the weekends.

331
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:56,480
You are going to help Grandma.

332
00:14:57,240 --> 00:14:58,120
A sound plan.

333
00:14:59,030 --> 00:15:01,200
You all had this planned.

334
00:15:03,790 --> 00:15:04,390
All right.

335
00:15:04,390 --> 00:15:05,080
Let's go.

336
00:15:05,080 --> 00:15:05,600
Start playing.

337
00:15:05,600 --> 00:15:06,630
Come on.

338
00:15:06,630 --> 00:15:07,390
Let's go.

339
00:15:16,750 --> 00:15:17,790
Mingyu.

340
00:15:18,270 --> 00:15:19,390
Xu Hong told me

341
00:15:19,390 --> 00:15:20,750
