348
00:15:38,960 --> 00:15:39,600
All right.

349
00:15:41,240 --> 00:15:42,630
This is 1500 yuan.

350
00:15:43,480 --> 00:15:43,960
Take it.

351
00:15:44,630 --> 00:15:45,750
