That's just sad.

366
00:16:07,480 --> 00:16:07,840
Right?

367
00:16:07,840 --> 00:16:08,720
No one should be left out.

368
00:16:09,510 --> 00:16:10,720
Fine.

369
00:16:10,720 --> 00:16:11,910
