403
00:17:05,350 --> 00:17:06,000
One ticket

404
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:07,070
is for me,

405
00:17:07,070 --> 00:17:07,480
the other

406
00:17:07,480 --> 00:17:08,400
is for someone else.

407
00:17:11,070 --> 00:17:12,480
Given our friendship,

408
00:17:12,790 --> 00:17:13,590
you're better off

409
00:17:13,590 --> 00:17:14,920
giving me the ticket.

410
00:17:15,790 --> 00:17:16,920
I thought you weren't interested.

411
00:17:17,510 --> 00:17:19,110
I'll do your homework for a month.

412
00:17:20,200 --> 00:17:20,790
Bye.

413
00:17:23,750 --> 00:17:24,440
Two months.

414
00:17:24,440 --> 00:17:25,070
Deal.

