00:17:27,830 --> 00:17:29,070
Everybody!

417
00:17:29,070 --> 00:17:30,200
Beijing,

418
00:17:30,550 --> 00:17:31,680
here I come!

419
00:17:34,590 --> 00:17:36,590
Beijing

420
00:17:36,590 --> 00:17:38,160
welcomes you!

421
00:17:38,160 --> 00:17:39,160
The world is ready

422
00:17:39,160 --> 00:17:40,720
for your arrival.

423
00:17:40,720 --> 00:17:42,270
The flowing...

424
00:17:42,270 --> 00:17:45,310
