425
00:17:45,310 --> 00:17:46,480
Beijing

426
00:17:46,480 --> 00:17:47,960
welcomes you!

427
00:17:47,960 --> 00:17:50,720
Surpass the top scores

428
00:17:50,720 --> 00:17:52,240
