485
00:19:32,790 --> 00:19:33,480
Give it back.

486
00:19:33,480 --> 00:19:34,000
Come on.

487
00:19:34,000 --> 00:19:35,310
They suit me the best.

488
00:19:35,310 --> 00:19:36,400
I'll take a photo for you.

489
00:19:39,480 --> 00:19:41,110
