531
00:20:57,160 --> 00:20:59,110
I want my Stefanie.

532
00:20:59,110 --> 00:21:00,030
Fine.

533
00:21:00,400 --> 00:21:01,310
Yingzi!

534
00:21:01,750 --> 00:21:02,350
What's the fuss?

535
00:21:02,350 --> 00:21:03,200
What happened?

536
00:21:03,200 --> 00:21:04,200
Why are you two fighting?

537
00:21:04,200 --> 00:21:05,200
