538
00:21:06,160 --> 00:21:07,750
Were you two late?

539
00:21:11,400 --> 00:21:12,070
Yingzi.

540
00:21:12,070 --> 00:21:12,720
It's all right.

541
00:21:12,720 --> 00:21:13,160
If you're late,

542
00:21:13,160 --> 00:21:14,240
