543
00:21:15,000 --> 00:21:16,030
No.

544
00:21:16,030 --> 00:21:16,920
Ask him.

545
00:21:17,640 --> 00:21:18,440
What's wrong?

546
00:21:23,200 --> 00:21:24,680
