552
00:21:37,400 --> 00:21:38,270
It's better out here.

553
00:21:38,270 --> 00:21:38,920
Right?

554
00:21:38,920 --> 00:21:39,480
Yeah.

555
00:21:39,480 --> 00:21:40,350
Look.

556
00:21:40,350 --> 00:21:41,880
