591
00:22:51,400 --> 00:22:53,480
Any thoughts about your trip to Beijing?

592
00:22:57,960 --> 00:22:58,960
I think

593
00:23:00,070 --> 00:23:01,510
spending time with you guys

594
00:23:02,110 --> 00:23:03,160
