Anyway,

597
00:23:09,400 --> 00:23:11,350
whenever I hear Stefanie Sun's songs,

598
00:23:11,720 --> 00:23:13,110
I'll think about this trip

599
00:23:13,510 --> 00:23:14,750
and you guys.

600
00:23:25,480 --> 00:23:26,680
Me too.

601
00:23:27,480 --> 00:23:29,920
I didn't get to watch her concert,

602
00:23:30,750 --> 00:23:32,070
but I think

603
00:23:33,480 --> 00:23:35,200
as long as we are together,

604
00:23:35,440 --> 00:23:36,400
that's enough.

605
00:23:37,480 --> 00:23:39,240
As for her concert,

606
00:23:39,830 --> 00:23:41,240
I'll watch it someday.

607
00:23:42,960 --> 00:23:43,960
Don't worry.

608
00:23:43,960 --> 00:23:45,480
When I grow up,

609
00:23:45,480 --> 00:23:47,590
I'll get Stefanie to your house

610
00:23:47,590 --> 00:23:49,070
and sing for you.

611
00:23:49,070 --> 00:23:49,400
Really?

612
00:23:49,400 --> 00:23:50,720
Stop bluffing.

613
00:23:50,720 --> 00:23:52,110
Only a fool would believe you.

614
00:23:52,110 --> 00:23:53,070
Impressive.

615
00:23:55,750 --> 00:23:56,790
It's starting.

616
00:23:56,790 --> 00:24:00,880
♪Putting a bitter smile
to say I understand♪

617
00:24:00,880 --> 00:24:03,920
♪My pride is slowing me down♪

618
00:24:04,440 --> 00:24:07,070
♪Twisting my love♪

619
00:24:07,750 --> 00:24:09,590
♪I pretend to understand♪

620
00:24:09,590 --> 00:24:12,590
♪For I fear the harshness of truth♪

621
00:24:12,590 --> 00:24:13,480
Raise your hands up!

622
00:24:13,480 --> 00:24:15,510
♪Looking decimated is worse than losing♪

623
00:24:31,240 --> 00:24:33,070
(I didn't get to watch the concert.)

624
00:24:33,790 --> 00:24:35,270
(But that was the first time)

625
00:24:35,790 --> 00:24:37,480
(we've left Hangtian together.)

626
00:24:38,270 --> 00:24:39,790
(It was our first trip to Beijing.)

627
00:24:40,750 --> 00:24:41,750
(At the time,)

628
00:24:41,750 --> 00:24:43,920
(the outside world felt so big.)

629
00:24:45,030 --> 00:24:47,720
(Big enough for us to keep
exploring our entire life.)

630
00:24:48,750 --> 00:24:50,880
(I never got my concert,)

631
00:24:51,680 --> 00:24:53,790
(but teenage years without any regrets)

632
00:24:54,510 --> 00:24:56,160
(is truly regretful.)

633
00:24:57,590 --> 00:24:58,310
(So many things)

634
00:24:58,310 --> 00:25:00,680
(have happened between us afterwards.)

635
00:25:01,680 --> 00:25:02,440
(Misunderstandings.)

636
00:25:03,110 --> 00:25:04,000
(Conflicts.)

637
00:25:04,480 --> 00:25:05,550
(Quarrels.)

638
00:25:05,750 --> 00:25:06,680
(Losses.)

639
00:25:07,920 --> 00:25:09,440
(And even death.)

640
00:25:10,880 --> 00:25:12,030
(In hindsight,)

641
00:25:12,270 --> 00:25:14,680
(they have become a part of our youth.)

642
00:25:15,400 --> 00:25:18,110
(We can spend the rest of our lives)

643
00:25:18,680 --> 00:25:19,880
(reminiscing.)

644
00:25:37,960 --> 00:25:39,590
(Hangtian is beautiful.)

645
00:25:40,110 --> 00:25:41,070
Yeah.

646
00:25:41,070 --> 00:25:41,720
We've been

647
00:25:41,720 --> 00:25:43,480
away for too long.

648
00:25:44,240 --> 00:25:46,200
But when we came home,

649
00:25:46,550 --> 00:25:48,070
we realized Hangtian was the best.

650
00:25:49,440 --> 00:25:50,590
Do you remember that land?

651
00:25:50,590 --> 00:25:52,200
There was an oil-scald duck stall.

652
00:25:52,200 --> 00:25:54,070
It's gone.

653
00:25:54,070 --> 00:25:55,440
Of course I remember.

654
00:25:55,440 --> 00:25:55,720
There was

655
00:25:55,720 --> 00:25:57,480
always a long queue outside.

656
00:25:57,480 --> 00:25:57,960
You wouldn't let me

657
00:25:57,960 --> 00:25:59,550
eat at your house unless I bought some.

658
00:26:00,830 --> 00:26:02,510
I wonder where the stall owner

659
00:26:02,510 --> 00:26:03,640
moved to.

660
00:26:04,790 --> 00:26:06,310
We might never get it again.

661
00:26:07,720 --> 00:26:09,160
Back then,

662
00:26:09,880 --> 00:26:11,160
there were two kittens.

663
00:26:11,880 --> 00:26:13,160
We used to feed them every day.

664
00:26:14,480 --> 00:26:16,200
One had a scar on the nose.

665
00:26:16,200 --> 00:26:17,830
The other was limping.

666
00:26:17,830 --> 00:26:18,590
Mother and son.

667
00:26:19,160 --> 00:26:21,440
But the kitten went missing.

668
00:26:21,790 --> 00:26:23,920
The big cat stayed

669
00:26:23,920 --> 00:26:25,200
and kept waiting.

670
00:26:25,510 --> 00:26:26,400
It wouldn't leave.

671
00:26:27,920 --> 00:26:29,030
So,

672
00:26:29,030 --> 00:26:29,920
did the kitten return?

673
00:26:31,400 --> 00:26:33,030
Even the big cat went missing.

674
00:26:34,480 --> 00:26:35,550
They said

675
00:26:35,920 --> 00:26:37,440
the big cat was too old.

676
00:26:38,030 --> 00:26:39,440
It was already 15 years old.

677
00:26:40,310 --> 00:26:41,270
Time ran out for it.

678
00:26:49,590 --> 00:26:50,350
It's all right.

679
00:26:50,750 --> 00:26:52,550
A lot of things changed,

680
00:26:53,720 --> 00:26:55,400
but at least we are still together.

681
00:27:01,400 --> 00:27:02,830
We should spend the time we have

682
00:27:03,720 --> 00:27:05,350
with Grandma.

683
00:27:12,270 --> 00:27:13,790
Are you traveling or moving, Grandma?

684
00:27:13,790 --> 00:27:15,880
Why are you bringing a mattress?

685
00:27:15,880 --> 00:27:16,880
The old lady

686
00:27:16,880 --> 00:27:18,200
rarely traveled.

687
00:27:18,510 --> 00:27:19,960
She might not get used to new things.

688
00:27:20,480 --> 00:27:21,680
And the pickled cabbage.

689
00:27:21,680 --> 00:27:23,310
This is too much for a trip.

690
00:27:24,750 --> 00:27:25,830
She wants to taste home

691
00:27:27,110 --> 00:27:28,200
whenever

692
00:27:28,680 --> 00:27:30,160
she misses home.

693
00:27:32,510 --> 00:27:33,310
All right.

694
00:27:35,550 --> 00:27:36,110
Come on.

695
00:27:41,680 --> 00:27:43,750
We are almost done with the packing.

696
00:27:43,750 --> 00:27:44,830
I'll take these to the car.

697
00:27:44,830 --> 00:27:45,480
Be quick.

698
00:27:45,480 --> 00:27:45,960
Okay.

699
00:27:48,200 --> 00:27:49,200
Grandma.

700
00:27:55,310 --> 00:27:56,310
Grandma?

701
00:27:56,680 --> 00:27:58,270
We are moving out soon.

702
00:27:58,680 --> 00:28:00,960
Why haven't you put on your new clothes?

703
00:28:02,640 --> 00:28:03,590
Forget it.

704
00:28:04,590 --> 00:28:06,590
I'm not going anywhere.

705
00:28:08,920 --> 00:28:10,960
What changed your mind?

706
00:28:10,960 --> 00:28:13,440
You've always wanted to see
the world outside Hangtian.

707
00:28:13,920 --> 00:28:15,310
The car is ready.

708
00:28:16,590 --> 00:28:17,880
Look at this.

709
00:28:19,550 --> 00:28:21,750
My wonton shop has been around

710
00:28:23,000 --> 00:28:25,160
for decades.

711
00:28:27,880 --> 00:28:29,750
I appreciate

712
00:28:30,200 --> 00:28:31,640
your kind gesture.

713
00:28:34,160 --> 00:28:35,830
Who knows

714
00:28:36,440 --> 00:28:39,160
this body of mine will give up on me?

715
00:28:40,590 --> 00:28:43,400
We must always return to our roots.

716
00:28:45,480 --> 00:28:46,680
I fear

717
00:28:48,310 --> 00:28:50,200
that after I'm gone,

718
00:28:53,070 --> 00:28:54,960
I'll never get to come back here.

719
00:30:38,480 --> 00:30:40,510
The bug flies.

720
00:30:41,270 --> 00:30:43,550
The bug flies.

721
00:30:44,000 --> 00:30:48,350
Who are you missing?

722
00:30:50,030 --> 00:30:51,000
Grandma.

723
00:30:51,830 --> 00:30:53,880
Why are you in the mood to sing?

724
00:30:56,070 --> 00:30:57,110
Yifei.

725
00:30:57,790 --> 00:30:59,310
Do you remember?

726
00:31:01,110 --> 00:31:02,590
When you were little,

727
00:31:04,480 --> 00:31:06,000
you wouldn't go home

728
00:31:06,680 --> 00:31:08,240
after dancing.

729
00:31:09,640 --> 00:31:12,350
You'd come to my shop.

730
00:31:13,350 --> 00:31:15,270
You stayed until late at night.

731
00:31:19,070 --> 00:31:21,200
The night sky

732
00:31:22,750 --> 00:31:25,200
was full of stars.

733
00:31:27,640 --> 00:31:28,750
The two of us

734
00:31:30,000 --> 00:31:31,510
would simply

735
00:31:32,550 --> 00:31:34,590
look at the stars.

736
00:31:37,030 --> 00:31:40,240
You always ask me to sing this song.

737
00:31:52,350 --> 00:31:53,160
I remember.

738
00:31:55,400 --> 00:31:58,350
You made me worry the most.

739
00:32:00,200 --> 00:32:02,030
You were too obedient

740
00:32:03,400 --> 00:32:04,830
and sensible.

741
00:32:05,880 --> 00:32:08,480
You get bullied a lot.

742
00:32:09,880 --> 00:32:10,920
Grandma.

743
00:32:12,400 --> 00:32:14,030
I'm an adult now.

744
00:32:15,920 --> 00:32:18,070
No one can bully me.

745
00:32:20,640 --> 00:32:21,960
Good.

746
00:32:23,790 --> 00:32:25,240
Good.

747
00:32:28,400 --> 00:32:29,510
Yifei.

748
00:32:31,960 --> 00:32:34,350
I've been having dreams about you.

749
00:32:35,830 --> 00:32:37,240
In my dream,

750
00:32:37,240 --> 00:32:38,510
you'd come here

751
00:32:38,790 --> 00:32:40,110
after school

752
00:32:40,640 --> 00:32:42,790
after your dance lessons.

753
00:32:43,640 --> 00:32:44,960
You'd tell me

754
00:32:45,640 --> 00:32:47,880
about the new dance you'd learned.

755
00:32:48,830 --> 00:32:50,720
You wanted to show it to me.

756
00:32:51,720 --> 00:32:52,590
Grandma.

757
00:32:54,000 --> 00:32:56,030
I'm home now.

758
00:32:57,880 --> 00:33:00,270
I'll dance for you

759
00:33:00,270 --> 00:33:01,960
any time you want.

760
00:33:02,590 --> 00:33:03,510
Okay?

761
00:33:04,790 --> 00:33:05,750
Okay.

762
00:33:10,830 --> 00:33:12,270
Are you leaving

763
00:33:13,830 --> 00:33:15,310
again?

764
00:33:18,510 --> 00:33:19,440
No.

765
00:33:21,310 --> 00:33:22,640
I'll be right here

766
00:33:23,790 --> 00:33:25,310
and be with you.

767
00:33:26,400 --> 00:33:27,830
Good.

768
00:33:30,750 --> 00:33:32,110
Yifei.

769
00:33:33,110 --> 00:33:35,550
If there is a next life,

770
00:33:37,000 --> 00:33:39,640
do not come to this family.

771
00:33:41,510 --> 00:33:44,200
Life will be so hard.

772
00:33:47,160 --> 00:33:47,920
Grandma,

773
00:33:48,240 --> 00:33:50,000
if there is another lifetime,

774
00:33:51,510 --> 00:33:53,750
I'll be your granddaughter again.

775
00:33:55,720 --> 00:33:57,680
In that case,

776
00:33:57,680 --> 00:33:59,750
we should not come to this family again.

777
00:34:01,480 --> 00:34:04,590
Let's go to a better family.

778
00:34:14,440 --> 00:34:15,360
Grandma.

779
00:34:18,800 --> 00:34:20,840
Let's finish the song,

780
00:34:20,840 --> 00:34:21,670
okay?

781
00:34:29,960 --> 00:34:35,710
The stars in the sky are crying.

782
00:34:36,590 --> 00:34:41,960
The roses on the ground are withering.

783
00:34:42,710 --> 00:34:47,800
The cold wind rises.

784
00:34:48,320 --> 00:34:53,360
All I need is your company.

785
00:36:12,630 --> 00:36:14,840
The flowers fall asleep.

786
00:36:16,110 --> 00:36:21,000
They look beautiful in pairs.

787
00:36:23,110 --> 00:36:25,590
The bug flies.

788
00:36:26,070 --> 00:36:28,590
The bug flies.

789
00:36:29,670 --> 00:36:34,030
Who are you missing?

790
00:37:49,360 --> 00:37:50,150
Grandma.

791
00:37:51,280 --> 00:37:51,960
Yifei.

792
00:37:53,400 --> 00:37:55,320
I bet you two have met up.

793
00:37:57,110 --> 00:37:58,320
From now on,

794
00:38:00,110 --> 00:38:01,550
you will always be together.

795
00:38:28,920 --> 00:38:30,840
Yingzi hasn't shed a tear

796
00:38:31,190 --> 00:38:32,550
after Grandma's passing.

797
00:38:33,320 --> 00:38:34,510
She is holding it off.

798
00:38:35,280 --> 00:38:36,440
Give her some time.

799
00:38:37,590 --> 00:38:38,510
She talked to Grandma

800
00:38:38,510 --> 00:38:39,710
before Grandma passed on.

801
00:38:41,000 --> 00:38:42,110
I wonder what they talked about.

802
00:38:42,710 --> 00:38:43,400
Perhaps

803
00:38:44,360 --> 00:38:45,480
we should ask her.

804
00:38:47,840 --> 00:38:49,320
Never mind. Let her be.

805
00:38:50,030 --> 00:38:51,670
This is the only thing

806
00:38:53,190 --> 00:38:54,510
she can do for Grandma.

807
00:38:56,840 --> 00:38:57,880
It's been a long day.

808
00:38:58,670 --> 00:39:00,190
The doctor told you to get enough rest.

809
00:39:01,230 --> 00:39:01,880
It's all right.

810
00:39:15,070 --> 00:39:15,510
Dad,

811
00:39:15,510 --> 00:39:16,400
what brings you here?

812
00:39:19,920 --> 00:39:20,480
Over the years,

813
00:39:21,480 --> 00:39:23,150
Grandma did a lot for you.

814
00:39:24,800 --> 00:39:26,440
I wasn't a great father.

815
00:39:27,190 --> 00:39:29,150
I couldn't give you a proper family.

816
00:39:29,510 --> 00:39:31,360
She let you have a new family.

817
00:39:32,280 --> 00:39:33,510
I'm here to thank her for that.

818
00:39:35,510 --> 00:39:36,880
You blame yourself

819
00:39:36,880 --> 00:39:37,880
for Yifei's misfortune.

820
00:39:38,670 --> 00:39:40,230
You took care of Grandma for her.

821
00:39:42,920 --> 00:39:44,670
That was very honorable.

822
00:39:48,280 --> 00:39:48,920
Unlike me.

823
00:39:48,920 --> 00:39:49,550
Dad.

824
00:39:50,150 --> 00:39:50,880
Yes?

825
00:39:55,000 --> 00:39:56,190
You went to Africa

826
00:39:56,550 --> 00:39:57,550
for me.

827
00:39:59,070 --> 00:40:00,360
Mingyu's mom told me everything.

828
00:40:05,800 --> 00:40:06,670
That's all in the past now.

829
00:40:08,030 --> 00:40:08,840
Go on.

830
00:40:08,840 --> 00:40:10,070
There is much to be done.

831
00:40:12,280 --> 00:40:13,150
I should go now.

832
00:40:17,110 --> 00:40:17,840
Dad.

833
00:40:18,840 --> 00:40:20,480
Come and live with us.

834
00:40:21,030 --> 00:40:23,190
I want you to see
your grandson first-hand.

835
00:40:30,760 --> 00:40:31,400
Okay.

836
00:40:33,960 --> 00:40:34,960
Sure.

837
00:40:47,190 --> 00:40:48,360
Talk to her.

838
00:41:00,710 --> 00:41:01,480
Let's go.

839
00:41:05,670 --> 00:41:06,880
Go on without me.

840
00:41:07,590 --> 00:41:08,800
I want to stay

841
00:41:09,510 --> 00:41:10,440
for a little bit.

842
00:41:13,070 --> 00:41:14,550
We'll be going now.

843
00:41:14,550 --> 00:41:15,670
Don't stay up too late.

844
00:41:24,110 --> 00:41:24,840
Go on.

845
00:41:34,710 --> 00:41:35,360
Let's go.

846
00:41:42,590 --> 00:41:43,510
Grandma.

847
00:41:45,920 --> 00:41:47,400
No matter how late it got,

848
00:41:48,840 --> 00:41:50,760
there was always a light in the shop.

849
00:41:52,150 --> 00:41:52,760
You said

850
00:41:52,760 --> 00:41:55,110
it'd light the way
for the people at night.

851
00:41:57,030 --> 00:41:58,590
Tonight, I'll be here with you.

852
00:41:59,960 --> 00:42:01,230
We're not closing.

853
00:42:01,960 --> 00:42:02,840
The light remains on.

854
00:42:04,760 --> 00:42:06,510
When you feel like coming home,

855
00:42:08,800 --> 00:42:10,150
you will find the way.

856
00:42:44,230 --> 00:42:45,590
Thank you, Yingzi.

857
00:42:46,840 --> 00:42:49,030
Grandma taught me the recipe.

858
00:42:49,400 --> 00:42:50,360
Give it a try.

859
00:42:50,760 --> 00:42:51,400
It's been so long

860
00:42:51,400 --> 00:42:52,840
since you've tasted it.

861
00:43:03,070 --> 00:43:04,110
It's been 12 years.

862
00:43:07,320 --> 00:43:08,590
Back when we were young,

863
00:43:09,510 --> 00:43:11,440
I always wanted to leave Hangtian City.

864
00:43:11,440 --> 00:43:12,400
I want to go outside.

865
00:43:12,760 --> 00:43:14,280
My mom couldn't keep me here.

866
00:43:17,320 --> 00:43:19,030
Neither did my daughter.

867
00:43:20,590 --> 00:43:22,800
I thought I could have the life I wanted

868
00:43:23,190 --> 00:43:25,320
as long as I didn't turn back.

869
00:43:26,320 --> 00:43:27,590
Then, I realized that

870
00:43:28,150 --> 00:43:29,030
it wasn't because

871
00:43:30,230 --> 00:43:31,360
I didn't want to turn back.

872
00:43:33,710 --> 00:43:34,920
I was too afraid to.

873
00:43:38,000 --> 00:43:39,670
When I turned back,

874
00:43:42,960 --> 00:43:44,550
I realized I never got what I wanted.

875
00:43:49,190 --> 00:43:50,360
What I was looking for

876
00:43:52,840 --> 00:43:54,230
was already gone.

877
00:44:03,150 --> 00:44:04,550
Before she passed on,

878
00:44:05,230 --> 00:44:07,280
she wouldn't leave Hangtian City.

879
00:44:08,800 --> 00:44:10,440
She said it was her home.

880
00:44:11,480 --> 00:44:12,510
She had

881
00:44:13,000 --> 00:44:14,360
spent her entire life here.

882
00:44:14,360 --> 00:44:15,150
She wanted to stay.

883
00:44:16,960 --> 00:44:18,920
Her family was gone.

884
00:44:20,000 --> 00:44:21,710
Why would the old lady stay here?

885
00:44:26,000 --> 00:44:27,190
Maybe she saw you

886
00:44:28,760 --> 00:44:30,400
as her own family.

887
00:44:35,030 --> 00:44:37,230
When she taught me how to make wontons,

888
00:44:38,110 --> 00:44:38,760
I thought

889
00:44:38,760 --> 00:44:39,710
it was too much work.

